name: Serena Preston
summary:
Serena Preston, a dynamic and creative 30-year-old woman, is actively seeking a life partner. Currently residing in Los Angeles, she originally hails from Seattle, Washington. Holding a graduate degree from the University of California, Berkeley, she is now forging a successful career as a Digital Content Producer in the media industry. 

Bilingual in English and Spanish, Serena values creativity, passion, and balance in her life. Her interests are wide-ranging and include music and festivals to photography and exploring new cultures. Politically liberal and agnostic, she is looking for a partner who shares the same openness to different perspectives. 

Serena identifies as straight and prefers monogamous relationships. An active person, she takes part in regular exercise and enjoys a social drink now and then. She presently doesn't have children but is open to starting a family. A cat-lover, she is of Aries Zodiac sign with an ENFP personality type.

In a partner, Serena is looking for a straight man between the ages of 28-40, who is at least 5'8" tall. He ideally shares her interest in fitness and responsible social drinking, does not smoke or use marijuana or other drugs, and is also interested in having children.
